data.description: Welcome to Sol de Villa Ranch, home of the Mari Family's Arabian Horses since the 1970's.  Purchased to have more room for their horses, this 4.75 acre parcel became a part of the dream of this long time Valley family.  Take a step back in time, as you wander down the long Pepper tree-lined driveway, along the moss-covered old fences and beautiful, level fields of pasture land.  Classic old wooden barn with large stalls, turnouts, tack room, covered aisle, and attached 1 bedroom, 1 bath guest house.  Further down the drive, pass the equipment shop/garage, the hay barn, and around the circle driveway to find the original 2 bedroom/2 bath Ranch-style house with enclosed sunroom and 2-car garage.  Property is on a shared well with 2 other parcels.  Trust sale, no showings for the first 21 days as Coming Soon Status.  Showings will start on November 1st  and continue through November 12th.  Any and all offers due by 5pm November 12th.  Trustee will respond to offers by 5pm November 15th.  Please do not go onto the property, Do not disturb occupants.  In essence, no trespassing please.
